# 7. キミの顔

Male Student A: Man, I'm beat.
Male Student B: Same here. I heard there's an after-party later, but I dunno if I'll go.
Male Student C: Yeah, me neither. I'm kinda tired.
Ena: (Are they...daytime students...?)
Ena: (If there are people here, maybe we should find somewhere—)
Male Student A: By the way, was that Akiyama running in the corridor just now?
Male Student B: Yeah, I think so.
Male Student C: Akiyama'd be pretty cute if it weren't for...y'know.
Ena: (Are they talking about Mizuki...?)
Ena: (I mean, Mizuki is good-looking, you'd have to admit.)
Male Student B: Ugh, cut it out man...
Male Student C: C'mon, am I wrong?
Male Student A: Hm? Is somebody there...?
Male Student A: Oh! Weren't you going around with Akiyama today?
Ena: ...!
Ena: (Shoot, they're talking to me.)
Ena: Um, hello. Yes, I was...
Male Student A: See? I was right!
Male Student B: Cool it man, what are you doing getting in her face like that? You're weirding her out.
Male Student A: C'mon, where's your festival spirit? I haven't seen you much around here. Are you a pal of Akiyama's?
Ena: Well... We've known each other for a while now.
Male Student A: Wow, really? Oh, then...
Male Student A: Does that mean you're also a dude?
Ena: ...
Ena: Huh?
Male Student B: Hey, quit it...!
Male Student A: C'mon, it was just a joke. Hahaha, sorry.
Ena: What's your problem?
Ena: A joke...? It wasn't funny at all.
Male Student A: Hey, I said I was sorry. I'm sure you're actually a regular girl—
Ena: ...? What's that supposed to mean?
Male Student A: Huh...?
Ena: What do you mean, “regular”...?
Male Student C: H-Hey, I think she seriously doesn't know...
Male Student B: I told you to cut it out!
Male Student A: B-But, she said they've known each other for a while. Why wouldn't she know?!
Male Student A: It's not like Akiyama hides it!
Ena: Wait...
Ena: (It's not...a joke...?)
Ena: (Wait... What...?)
Ena: (So...)
Ena: (That means...)
Ena: (The thing Mizuki wanted to discuss...)
Male Student A: Ack...!
Ena: ...?!
Mizuki: Oh...
Mizuki: ...
Ena: ...!
Ena: Wait, Mizuki!!!
